A massive, towering maze constructed from thousands of tangled legal documents, contracts, and fine print papers, rendered in vintage 1950s advertising illustration style with muted yellows, teals, and warm oranges. A tiny figure in a business suit stands at the entrance looking overwhelmed, while another figure on the opposite side holds giant scissors, cutting a clean, simple path straight through the chaos. Paper fragments float in the air like confetti. The maze casts dramatic shadows across a warm cream-colored background, giving the scene depth and a sense of bureaucratic absurdity mixed with hopeful liberation.
